      {
        "id": "25",
        "title": "Facebook Groups Posting",
        "description": "Add posting to relevant Facebook investing/trading groups. Facebook Groups get significantly higher organic reach than profile posts â€” this is the main distribution channel on Facebook. Implementation: (1) Research and join 5-10 relevant groups (investing, trading education, financial freedom, side hustle). (2) Add group posting to the auto-poster â€” post to 1-2 groups per day, rotating through the list. (3) Content must be pure value, no self-promotion â€” groups have moderators who will ban promotional accounts. (4) Adapt post format for group culture (more conversational, question-ending posts that invite discussion). Group posts are separate from profile posts â€” this adds to the Facebook posting volume.",
