        "title": "TradingView Content Auto-Posting",
        "description": "Auto-post educational ideas and analyses to TradingView. User has 357 followers and it's the monetization platform (free indicators â†’ paid subscriptions). Staying active on TradingView drives indicator discovery and builds credibility. Implementation: (1) Automate posting TradingView ideas (educational chart analyses). (2) Repurpose backtest results and strategy breakdowns from other platforms. (3) Post 1-2 ideas per week â€” quality matters more than volume on TradingView. (4) Link to free indicators in ideas to drive downloads. TradingView has its own web editor â€” will need Playwright automation for posting.",
