      {
        "id": "27",
        "title": "Analytics Dashboard â€” Automate Weekly Review Data Pull",
        "description": "Build a dashboard that auto-pulls metrics from all 4 platforms (X, Reddit, LinkedIn, Facebook) into one view for the weekly performance review. Currently the weekly review requires manually checking each platform. This dashboard aggregates: impressions, engagement rate, likes, comments, shares, follows gained per post. Ranks top 5 and bottom 5 posts. Identifies patterns (best pillar, hook style, format, posting time). Generates a summary report. Could be a new page in the existing review dashboard (localhost:5111) or a standalone tool. Data sources: platform APIs or scraping.",
