      {
        "id": "29",
        "title": "Email List + Lead Magnet for Monetization Funnel",
        "description": "Critical missing piece in the monetization funnel. Current funnel: free content â†’ free TradingView indicators â†’ \\0/month subscription. The gap: no way to capture emails between free content and paid conversion. A lead magnet (e.g., '5 Indicators Every Beginner Needs' PDF, free email course, or strategy guide) collects emails and gives a direct channel to convert followers into subscribers. Implementation: (1) Create a lead magnet (downloadable resource). (2) Build a simple landing page for email capture. (3) Set up email collection (ConvertKit, Mailchimp, or similar). (4) Add occasional soft CTAs in social posts pointing to the lead magnet. (5) Build a simple email nurture sequence (3-5 emails over 2 weeks) that leads to the \\0/month offer.",
        "details": "",
        "testStrategy": "",
        "status": "deferred",
